but you think he's still alive?

787
00:55:20,250 --> 00:55:21,478
He was still alive.

788
00:55:22,218 --> 00:55:23,185
Still alive.

789
00:55:24,788 --> 00:55:26,881
You made a phone call. Who did you call?

790
00:55:26,990 --> 00:55:29,117
-I called his mother.
-What'd you tell her?

791
00:55:29,559 --> 00:55:31,993
-Hello?
-What is it, Susan?

792
00:55:33,530 --> 00:55:36,397
-ls everything all right?
-Jeff and I had a fight.

793
00:55:36,900 --> 00:55:37,867
And...

794
00:55:39,235 --> 00:55:40,532
He was on drugs.

795
00:55:41,671 --> 00:55:44,868
And he hurt me. And he hit Andrew.

796
00:55:46,209 --> 00:55:48,177
And he took his keys and he left.

797
00:55:48,278 --> 00:55:49,711
What are you talking about?

798
00:55:53,416 --> 00:55:56,817
So you lied to his mother
about the keys and about him leaving?

799
00:55:57,053 --> 00:55:58,452
No, that was real to me.

800
00:55:58,555 --> 00:55:59,954
It was real and he was still alive.

801
00:56:00,523 --> 00:56:01,547
After you hung up

802
00:56:03,026 --> 00:56:05,221
what'd you do with the rest ofyour night?

803
00:56:07,130 --> 00:56:08,097
I waited.

804
00:56:08,598 --> 00:56:10,589
And I watched for Jeff to get back up.

805
00:56:10,867 --> 00:56:14,064
Because I knew that
the second that I went to sleep,

806
00:56:14,671 --> 00:56:15,763
he was gonna get up

807
00:56:16,206 --> 00:56:19,141
and he was gonna come inside
and he was gonna try and get me.

808
00:56:20,744 --> 00:56:21,904
So I stayed awake.

809
00:56:37,994 --> 00:56:40,292
She was one busy lady

810
00:56:40,397 --> 00:56:42,524
that week of lies and fabrication,

811
00:56:42,632 --> 00:56:46,033
trying so hard to pretend
that Jeffrey just walked out on her.

812
00:56:46,136 --> 00:56:48,229
On her and his children.

813
00:56:48,538 --> 00:56:50,563
They say post traumatic stress syndrome.

814
00:56:51,508 --> 00:56:53,442
How about "cover your tail syndrome"?

815
00:57:01,885 --> 00:57:03,944
One more thing. One more thing.

816
00:57:04,687 --> 00:57:06,279
One more thing.

817
00:57:06,389 --> 00:57:07,947
I just got to grab this.

818
00:57:08,591 --> 00:57:09,751
Susan?

819
00:57:09,859 --> 00:57:11,190
Hey, Susan!

820
00:57:12,362 --> 00:57:14,523
-Hi.
