822
00:57:21,204 --> 00:57:22,364
Got it.

823
00:57:22,472 --> 00:57:24,599
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

824
00:57:24,974 --> 00:57:25,963
-Okay.
-Bye.

825
00:57:26,209 --> 00:57:27,335
See you later. Bye!

826
00:57:27,544 --> 00:57:29,569
Bye.

827
00:57:29,679 --> 00:57:30,839
Let's get another bag.

828
00:57:31,648 --> 00:57:33,809
