830
00:57:39,055 --> 00:57:41,523
Well, then I'd like to withdraw some money.

831
00:57:41,624 --> 00:57:42,955
Okay. How much?

832
00:57:43,827 --> 00:57:44,794
All of it.

833
00:57:45,295 --> 00:57:46,956
Where's Daddy?

