976
01:08:28,971 --> 01:08:29,995
No!

977
01:08:30,840 --> 01:08:33,434
Breaking news, live from Harris County.

978
01:08:33,576 --> 01:08:35,237
We are outside the residence of a...

979
01:08:35,344 --> 01:08:37,608
