980
01:08:41,450 --> 01:08:44,647
The wife reported domestic violence
to a neighbor on Wednesday.

981
01:08:44,787 --> 01:08:46,652
The Fourth Precinct has a record
of her coming in

982
01:08:46,755 --> 01:08:48,154
and telling her story on the same day.

983
01:08:48,290 --> 01:08:50,884
So they issued a warrant for his arrest
and a restraining order.

984
01:08:50,993 --> 01:08:52,358
So this is a domestic dispute.

985
01:08:53,395 --> 01:08:54,521
She gonna say self-defense?

986
01:08:54,630 --> 01:08:56,530
If he came back that night,
it could have happened like this.

987
01:08:56,899 --> 01:08:58,059
Tell him what you just told me.

988
01:08:58,434 --> 01:08:59,662
We rolled him before we bagged him.

989
01:08:59,768 --> 01:09:01,497
Almost every stab wound was on his front.

990
01:09:01,804 --> 01:09:03,328
There's no defensive wounds
on his hands at all.

991
01:09:13,015 --> 01:09:15,916
So the last time he's at work,
or anybody talked to him, was Monday night.

992
01:09:16,018 --> 01:09:18,145
Except she told the in-laws
she'd seen him Tuesday morning.

993
01:09:18,287 --> 01:09:19,481
Yeah, but they didn't see him.

994
01:09:19,788 --> 01:09:23,781
The only person that can confirm seeing him
after Monday night was the wife.

995
01:09:24,360 --> 01:09:26,294
-What do we know about him?
-He's got some priors.

996
01:09:26,529 --> 01:09:29,123
Felony conviction for controlled substance.

997
01:09:29,231 --> 01:09:30,255
Marijuana.

998
01:09:30,366 --> 01:09:31,390
And he's got...

999
01:09:31,567 --> 01:09:32,659
Felony assault charge.

1000
01:09:32,768 --> 01:09:34,895
Brandy Davenport, ex fiance.

1001
01:09:35,171 --> 01:09:36,229
So this is a pattern?

1002
01:09:36,639 --> 01:09:37,606
Signs seem to point to it.

1003
01:09:37,706 --> 01:09:39,037
Well, let's just say that's how it happened.

1004
01:09:39,141 --> 01:09:40,130
Monday night, he beats her up.

1005
01:09:40,242 --> 01:09:43,234
Tuesday morning,
he comes back for another shot.

1006
01:09:43,345 --> 01:09:45,336
Wednesday, she goes to the police,
files a report.

1007
01:09:45,447 --> 01:09:47,506
He finds out about it,
he comes back for revenge.

1008
01:09:47,650 --> 01:09:49,641
They go at it, she gets a knife and...

1009
01:09:50,586 --> 01:09:51,780
And it all goes to hell.

1010
01:09:52,354 --> 01:09:54,049
Battered wife, angry husband?

1011
01:09:55,124 --> 01:09:57,388
What do you do after you've just
killed someone in self defense?

1012
01:09:57,726 --> 01:09:58,920
-Call the cops.
-Exactly.

1013
01:09:59,028 --> 01:10:00,825
You're not gonna spend a week
trying to cover it up.

1014
01:10:01,463 --> 01:10:03,226
-Maybe she panicked.
-For a week?

1015
01:10:03,666 --> 01:10:05,827
Then got her lawyer to put her in hiding?

1016
01:10:06,101 --> 01:10:07,363
He's here.

1017
01:10:07,870 --> 01:10:08,837
-What?
-He's here.

1018
01:10:08,971 --> 01:10:11,769
No, no, no.
That's your attorney, Mrs. Wright.

1019
01:10:13,542 --> 01:10:15,009
Okay, okay.

1020
01:10:16,645 --> 01:10:18,237
What? What is it?

1021
01:10:20,249 --> 01:10:21,238
No.

1022
01:10:24,086 --> 01:10:25,849
He was sleeping.

1023
01:10:26,322 --> 01:10:28,415
And there was a knife.

1024
