1278
01:24:26,961 --> 01:24:28,394
Please be seated, ladies and gentlemen.

1279
01:24:49,050 --> 01:24:52,042
In the State of Texas
v. Susan Lucille Wright,

1280
01:24:52,153 --> 01:24:54,314
