1285
01:25:05,700 --> 01:25:08,430
Does the defendant
wish to say anything at this time?

1286
01:25:08,536 --> 01:25:09,901
No, Your Honor.

1287
01:25:16,111 --> 01:25:17,510
You have to let go, sorry.

1288
01:25:18,246 --> 01:25:20,009
Got to take you away now, sorry.

1289
01:25:21,182 --> 01:25:22,206
Right this way.

1290
01:25:45,173 --> 01:25:46,606
Self defense, really?

1291
01:25:47,108 --> 01:25:49,133
Only two people know the answer to that.

1292
01:26:21,342 --> 01:26:23,276
Come on, your lawyer's waiting.

1293
01:26:26,414 --> 01:26:27,574
This way please.

1294
01:26:44,632 --> 01:26:45,997
Hello, Susan.

1295
01:26:47,035 --> 01:26:48,229
Hello.

1296
01:26:49,404 --> 01:26:50,962
