1302
01:27:08,223 --> 01:27:10,020
I don't think you got a fair trial.

1303
01:27:10,358 --> 01:27:11,586
I can tell you that.

1304
01:27:12,293 --> 01:27:14,284
So I wanna ask you more questions.

1305
01:27:15,530 --> 01:27:17,760
I need to know more about Susan Wright.

1306
01:27:20,134 --> 01:27:23,433
Well, hope you like me.

